ji\" /> <br />\n屋企太嘈溫唔到書日日到溫到好夜先返屋企，屋企個功能係賓館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打最緊要將所有負能量同恥辱化作動力，窮閪最恐怖就係無野事，為左上流不惜代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994fca2d7e1ed6100b9ea5e1ee152c8f0a29d73f","tid":129433,"uid":51748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮閪靠自己入港大法律同建立人脈跟資深大律師打遺產官司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到大學冇洗過屋企一個仙，出國打比賽自己出錢，乜都一腳踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企太嘈溫唔到書日日到溫到好夜先返屋企，屋企個功能係賓館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打最緊要將所有負能量同恥辱化作動力，窮閪最恐怖就係無野事，為左上流不惜代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個咁叻咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c7c99614ce196cbb7fb9496e7a736bd646658d","tid":129433,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:39:10.000Z","msg":"認真睇唔到未來<br />\n根本唔會有動力去上進<br />\n依家都係等雙親安享晚年後就正式完成任務<br />\n如果唔係我都一早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35f648177930c4220c7f4d6090de9d38e9a2c58","tid":129433,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e3bcd9f2d71e105d28948d66c1465ee2d720da2","tid":129433,"uid":53278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"邊撚個同你講入到大學就有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂 話就話爆煲姐 又未至於工都冇得做<br />\n最多咪食少d 洗撚去死咩"},{"pid":"792960fcc2c9765a8d87958b80e14029339ff1f8","tid":129433,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"考警仲好 鐵飯碗<br />\n（如果你唔係仇警憤青既話）"},{"pid":"8368791c5460a2a5c5966309856bb625058a3d3e","tid":129433,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14: